snippet.textDisplay:
If RDJ doesn't want to do anymore iron man for whatever reason then he had to do a role that is at least on par with Tony stark. He portrayed Tony as a flawed human with an overall good nature for himself and his family/ friends and the world.
I can't imagine a role he could do besides a good hearted political or business person.
I hope he doesn't do a villain role... oof.
